assets.description:
This is my first Scene in which I tried to tell a story, not just randomly draw with strokes in Tiltbrush :) (Danny Bittman Becoming a VR Artist Ep. 7)  

#city #futuristic #church #sect #night #cyberpunk #neon #night #environment #hunter

The story:
The soldiers car broke. Hes close to the futuristic sect town. The wolf follows him. Hes got surveillance towers in front of him, and a city you might never get away from again. . .But he cant go anywhere else
